tions":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@discardableResult"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"onNotifyUsername","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"flags","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"ConnectFlags","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ConnectFlagsV"},{"text":" = ConnectFlags(0), ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"handler"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"@escaping","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO17MountOperationRefV","kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/MountOperationRef","text":"MountOperationRef"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"ParamSpecRef","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ParamSpecRefV"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida","text":"Void"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Flags","type":"text"}]}],"name":"flags"},{"name":"handler","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The signal handler to call","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Run the given callback whenever the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"notifyUsername"},{"type":"text","text":" signal is emitted"}]}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note that getting this signal doesn’t itself guarantee that the value of"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"the property has actually changed. When it is emitted is determined by the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"derived GObject class. If the implementor did not create the property with"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"[explicit_notify](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/explicit_notify, then any call to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set_property()"},{"type":"text","text":" results"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"in "},{"code":"notify","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" being emitted, even if the new value is the same as the old.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"If they did pass [explicit_notify](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/explicit_notify, then this signal is emitted only","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"when they explicitly call "},{"code":"g_object_notify()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_notify_by_pspec()"},{"text":",","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and common practice is to do that only when the value has actually changed.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"This signal is typically used to obtain change notification for a","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"single property, by specifying the property name as a detail in the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_signal_connect()"},{"type":"text","text":" call, like this:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"(C Language Example):"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"C","type":"codeListing","code":["g_signal_connect (text_view->buffer, \"notify::paste-target-list\",","                  G_CALLBACK (gtk_text_view_target_list_notify),","                  text_view)"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"It is important to note that you must use","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"#class@GObject.ParamSpec#parameter-names"},{"type":"text","text":" as"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"detail strings for the notify signal."}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This represents the underlying "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"notify::username"},{"text":" signal","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"Note","style":"note","type":"aside"}],"kind":"content"}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/MountOperationRef\/onNotifyUsername(flags:handler:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"references":{"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/MountOperationRef":{"title":"MountOperationRef","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/gio\/mountoperationref","abstract":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GMountOperation"},{"text":" provides a mechanism for interacting with the user.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"It can be used for authenticating mountable operations, such as loop"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"mounting files, hard drive partitions or server locations. It can"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"also be used to ask the user questions or show a list of applications"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"preventing unmount or eject operations from completing."}],"type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"MountOperationRef"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/MountOperationRef","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MountOperationRef"}]},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/MountOperationRef/onNotifyUsername(flags:handler:)":{"role":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/gio\/mountoperationref\/onnotifyusername(flags:handler:)","title":"onNotifyUsername(flags:handler:)","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"onNotifyUsername","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"flags","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ConnectFlagsV","text":